commit message:
Code Cleanup and small UI updates
-removed unused functions and unnecessary comments
-removed EventList, not needed after switch to SQLite
-changed actionbar icons for the sub-activities
-changed title of untitled events to match android calendar

Updates Dialog UI Tweaks
-show dialog with changelog at first run (and after upgrades)
-changed notification icon
-tweaked launcher icon
-tweaked notification to display shorter date format

UI Updates, Donation Key Check
-new launcher icon
-new notification icon
-checks for installation of donation key
-adding web/ folder to hold resources for project website

Update Readme
-updated readme to include screenshots

Version 2.0.2
-Fixed lookahead interval to use the selected value.
-Fixed a bug where quick silence wouldn't cancel if the calendar provider changed while silencing was active
